article_metadata.description: On Fox News over the weekend, conservative commentator Laura Ingraham asked Gov. John Kasich whether he and President Barack Obama are “BFFs (best friends forever) for real?” After the Democratic president gave the Republican governor a rhetorical kiss on Thursday in Cleveland for expanding Medicaid coverage to 275,000 poor Ohioans, Ingraham suggested to Kasich, "You guys are tight."
